Package: opensand-core-all
Architecture: any
Depends: opensand-core-bin (= ${binary:Version})
Description: The OpenSAND emulation testbed core with all the configuration files
  OpenSAND is an emulation testbed aiming to represent in a cost effective way a
  satellite telecommunication system for research and engineering activities.

